STATE of North Carolina
v.
Juston Leon WILLIAMS No. 114P19 Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 29, 2019 Juston Leon Williams, for Williams, Juston Leon. Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, For State of N.C.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Defendant on the 28th of March 2019 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Onslow County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 29th of March 2019."
